        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Sweaty, hot Leo post packing struggles to think clearly. His thoughts loop around small items that seem to have gone missing. Once everything is in the car we go down to the idyllic beach and dive into the calm ocean. ",
            "link": null
          },
