    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Two kayaks and the African Sunset bring out a sense of peace that I must say is truly unrivalled. Lying back in the boat and looking up at the postal blue sky, my arms overhead; stretching into the water. My thoughts are quiet, far away voices - like the sound of children from over a hill. Colours, sensations and sounds abound. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
