          "plain_text": "Two kayaks and the African Sunset bring out a sense of peace that I must say is truly unrivalled. Lying back in the boat and looking up at the postal blue sky, my arms overhead; stretching into the water. My thoughts are quiet, far away voices - like the sound of children from over a hill. Colours, sensations and sounds abound. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
